{
  "name": "RPlog_Attacked_on_GDIStar",
  "title": "Attacked on GDIStar",
  "summary": "On the relaxed Observation Deck of the GDIStar dome, Lotus, the Horansi Kuxli, Piper, and Di'anCecht share a table while the cloaked Sithkassi assassin Sneer creeps closer, hissing 'Princess Leia' and brandishing an S-shaped blade. Mistaking the brown-haired Piper for Leia Organa, Sneer lunges and stabs Piper in the side before Lotus blasts him unconscious and Di'anCecht scrambles to staunch the bleeding. When the assassin twitches back to life still reaching for a knife, Lotus stuns him again and Kuxli savagely tears out his throat, killing him. The medic Rtufo arrives to treat Piper and evacuate her, and the investigator Inoga questions Lotus, who explains the attack appears to have been an attempt on Leia's life. While the aloof Alora watches the carnage with detached amusement over her wine, Inoga searches the corpse, files her report, and arranges to dine with Lotus the following evening, as Admiral Ackbar looks on.",
